chess.domain.board

Class ChessBoard

  • java.lang.Object
    • chess.domain.board.ChessBoard

  • public class ChessBoard
extends Object
    This class is responsible for keeping track of the current situation on board. This class also offers methods to access every piece on board and Squares they threaten or can move to.
    Author:
    sami
